{"tid":631361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"漏帶默書簿被罰留堂 中五女生打老師守行為一年","createTime":"2018-04-16T11:37:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T04:36:18.000Z","uid":44035,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"fc9bb344726000e1772350e8a8904382ca84e167","tid":631361,"uid":44035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T11:37:39.000Z","msg":"中五女生因漏帶默書簿回校，遭男老師罰留堂，女生激動起來，向老師揮拳再腳踢多次後離開，老師自行到醫院檢查，其前額紅腫擦傷，背部觸痛，女生其後於警誡下承認一時衝動犯案。案件今在觀塘法院再訊，被控一項襲擊致造成身體傷害罪的女生承認案情，獲准以1000元簽保守行為一年。<br />\n17歲中五女生劉慧詩原被控於去年10月31日在將軍澳圓玄學院第三中學班房內，襲擊54歲任教中文及宗教的男教師麥國全。<br />\n<br />\n法庭記者：潘琪慧<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.singtao.ca/toronto/2509531/2018-04-16/post-中五女生被罰留堂-打老師致額傷守行為一年/?variant=zh-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtao.ca%2Ftoronto%2F2509531%2F2018-04-16%2Fpost-%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%94%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E7%BD%B0%E7%95%99%E5%A0%82-%E6%89%93%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E8%87%B4%E9%A1%8D%E5%82%B7%E5%AE%88%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%2F%3Fvariant%3Dzh-hk&d=4FvlyEH6dK%2B%2FrrW2fqsZeL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=2bb744f0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.singtao.ca/toronto/2509531/2018-04-16/post-中五女生被罰留堂-打老師致額傷守行為一年/?variant=zh-hk</a>"},{"pid":"b093826f38d3508e4eaa11ad737d5a744e491867","tid":631361,"uid":47029,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T11:39:14.000Z","msg":"見到字都扯扯地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bce6b65134dd977ec328af398f0546e91bfb1f9","tid":631361,"uid":46835,"like":50,"dislike":5,"score":45,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T11:39:59.000Z","msg":"form 5 仲默書？！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412c857125b3dbbda82302acab13be85588d74b3","tid":631361,"uid":62494,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T11:43:27.000Z","msg":"我呢D成績好又扮乖既學生,就算平時唔返學唔交功課 D miss呀叔都唔敢奈我何<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c383c59b470347ac5fc38acaef843